  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Events Services Executive",
  "description": "<p>The <strong>Plattering Co</strong> delivers modern culinary experiences complete with a visual feast for the eyes. We are looking for a driven and creative lead to oversee the visual aesthetics for products across the company’s brands and to ensure the smooth delivery of styling services.</p><p><strong>Job description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lead the creative team including designers and stylists, culinary and operations departments for smooth delivery and order execution.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with clients and sales teams to understand event requirements, conceptualise and to propose styling products and services.  </p></li><li><p>Lead development of new experiences, styling themes, props, and visual concepts, keeping offerings fresh and competitive.</p></li><li><p>Lead creative planning and design for major events, customised client events and festive seasons, ensuring cohesive styling from concept to execution.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Work closely with operations to translate creative concepts into feasible production plans.</p></li><li><p>Maintain consistency in the brands’ aesthetic across products.</p></li><li><p>Provide on-site creative direction during key events to ensure vision integrity and smooth delivery and execution.</p></li><li><p>Maintain quality control over all creative deliverables.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with the management team to understand company direction to achieve collective goals across brands.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Possess a creative eye.</p></li><li><p>Possess 5-7 years of relevant work experience with experience in people management.</p></li></ul><p>To apply, please email your resume to hr@theplatteringco.com. Kindly note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
